        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         As all giants in the Arena summon, I doubt you'll be able to hunt here - at least efficiently - with only 2 52 necs. With a group of lvl 50+, it's cake. Just be prepared to stay there for a long time, robe is a rare drop (I saw 1 robe drop in Arena in about 20 hours of hunting). On a brighter note, you'll get some other armor quest pieces for you and your group while huntin there.</P><P>Good luck for you and don't forget you'll need at least to be kindly with the Coldain to get the quest reward.</P><P>Baroness Xenophore Doomscales<BR>Lvl 54 Iksar necro<BR>"Seigneurs de la Lune Noire", T.Marr<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
